Together with the owner all machines and inventory items belonging to the
owner have been deleted as well.

<%- if @softdelete -%>
As the soft-delete module is turned on the owner is fully restorable.
If the owner is being restored the related items (machines and inventory) will
be restored as well, IF the restore is being done within 10 minutes of the
deletion.

Link to restore: <%= deleted_owners_url %>
<%- else -%>
As the soft-delete module is turned off the owner is not restorable.
<%- end -%>
